# SafeSight-MLOps — Complete Tech Breakdown & Resume Guide

---

## 🏗️ Architecture Overview

SafeSight-MLOps (branded **Tasuke'26**) is a **multi-module, microservices-based** platform with two major products:

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "AI Engine (Python)"
        A1["YOLOv8 Pose Detection"]
        A2["Fall Detection State Machine"]
        A3["OpenCV Video Pipeline"]
    end

    subgraph "Web Dashboard (Node.js)"
        B1["Express.js REST API"]
        B2["Socket.io Real-time"]
        B3["Vanilla JS Frontend + Three.js"]
    end

    subgraph "MedFlow Module (React)"
        C1["Vite + TypeScript + React"]
        C2["MediaPipe Pose Estimation"]
        C3["Three.js 3D Body Model"]
        C4["Zustand State + GSAP Animations"]
    end

    subgraph "Infrastructure"
        D1["Docker + Docker Compose"]
        D2["MongoDB (Mongoose)"]
        D3["GitHub Actions CI/CD"]
        D4["Nginx Reverse Proxy"]
    end

    A1 --> B2
    A3 --> B2
    B2 --> B1
    B1 --> D2
    C1 --> B1
    C1 --> B2
    D1 --> B1
    D1 --> C1
    D1 --> D2
    D3 --> D1
```

